description:
Pixel Piracy is a side-scrolling 2d, real time strategy/sandbox/simulation game created by indie developer Vitali Kirpu and produced by Alexander Poysky.

In the game, the player leads the life of a pirate captain. Recruit a crew, outfit and customize your ship and set sail on the open seas. Don't forget your diapers!

Pixel Piracy Website: http://piracysim.com/
Steam Page: http://store.steampowered.com/app/264140/
